Text: Well, the sample was perfect picture quality. Sound was close to great. Not well seeded though. But patience is a virtue, right? If the full video is the same quality, you'll be on my top 10 list. Thanks ahead of time.
Actual video is NOT from the same source as the sample. Surprise surprise! Ltt_Fr1, how could you post a fake sample? You should be removed from this site.

The sample is definitely from the source. I had to go back an check myself because I was surprised by how dark it was in many scenes.

Good film though, and thanks. I'd just recommend that people follow Killawife's advice because this type of film demands a clearer picture IMO. It's not like Batman Begins where I could just write off a few seconds worth of relatively unimportant fight scenes, annoying though they were.

Thanks for the upload!  This movie has an interesting plot and would have liked to see a better copy somewhere, but...this is better than nothing.

Quality
A: 7/10
V: 5/10
